    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I take Jordan’s car and become a different driver in the streets of Joburg. Where once I would hit the brakes for a yellow light now I hit the accelerator. Driving with conviction is actually safer around these parts. At each red robot the fellow drivers on either side of you size you up, daring you to dice them. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
