          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I go to a Checkers FX because I’m a diehard fan. This one feel just like the one that I go to back in Cape Town and finding things is fairly simple. I’ve collected most of the items on my list when Simon calls. I’m wearing Jordan’s headphones so I can simply continue wondering the isles aimlessly while having a lovely catchup with him. ",
